#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/file_and_block.rst:2
msgid "File & Block"
msgstr "文件与块"

#: ../../source/mp/l2_storage/file_and_block.rst:4
msgid ""
"File-system and block-device backends that persist KV cache to local or "
"networked storage. These are conceptually similar -- they write KV "
"objects to files or fixed-size slots on a disk or block device."
msgstr "将 KV 缓存持久化到本地或网络存储的文件系统和块设备后端。二者在概念上相似——均将 KV 对象写入文件或磁盘、块设备上的固定大小槽位。"

